# Band Practice Webapp - Root Environment Variables
# This file shows the overall configuration for all services
# Copy relevant sections to each service's .env file

# =============================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT OVERVIEW
# =============================================================================
# This application consists of 3 services:
# 1. Frontend (React/Vite) - User interface
# 2. Backend (Node.js/Express) - API and YouTube processing  
# 3. Audio Processing Service (Python/Flask) - AI audio separation

# =============================================================================
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT SETUP
# =============================================================================
# Frontend: http://localhost:5173
# Backend: http://localhost:3001  
# Audio Processing: http://localhost:5001

# =============================================================================
# RAILWAY PRODUCTION SETUP
# =============================================================================
# Each service deployed separately with these configurations:

# Frontend Service:
# - Build Command: npm run build
# - Start Command: npm run preview
# - Environment: VITE_BACKEND_URL=https://your-backend.up.railway.app

# Backend Service:
# - Build Command: npm install
# - Start Command: npm start
# - Environment: 
#   - NODE_ENV=production
#   - AUDIO_PROCESSING_SERVICE_URL=http://audio-service.railway.internal:5001

# Audio Processing Service:
# - Build Command: pip install -r requirements.txt
# - Start Command: ./start.sh (uses Gunicorn)
# - Environment:
#   - BACKEND_URL=http://backend-service.railway.internal:3001

# =============================================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# =============================================================================
# - Use Railway private networking (.railway.internal) for service-to-service communication
# - Frontend must use public HTTPS URLs to avoid mixed content issues
# - Audio processing service uses htdemucs_6s model for 6-track separation
# - Minimum 8GB RAM recommended for audio processing service

# =============================================================================
# RAILWAY AUTOMATIC VARIABLES
# =============================================================================
# Railway automatically provides these variables:
# - PORT - Service port (different for each service)
# - RAILWAY_STATIC_URL - Public URL for the service
# - RAILWAY_PRIVATE_DOMAIN - Internal networking domain